maki-maki, maki-maki,
maki-maki, maki.

266
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:59,458
Maki-maki, maki-maki,

267
00:13:59,541 --> 00:14:01,458
maki-maki, maki-maki...

268
00:14:01,541 --> 00:14:03,666
[SHIHO, LILIE, YAYOI]
...maki-maki, maki-maki,

269
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:07,666
maki-maki, maki-maki, maki-maki.

270
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,666
[SHIHO, LILIE, YAYOI]
Maki-maki! Maki-maki! Maki-maki!

271
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:13,000
Maki-maki! Maki-maki! Maki-maki!

272
