Maki-maki!

276
00:14:23,041 --> 00:14:24,375
[BOTH]
Maki-maki...

277
00:14:24,458 --> 00:14:25,583
[SHIHO]
Maki-maki!

278
00:14:25,666 --> 00:14:26,916
[LILIE, YAYOI]
Maki-maki...

279
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,666
[SHIHO]
Maki-maki!

280
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,166
[yelps]

281
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,583
[SHIHO gasps]

282
00:14:30,666 --> 00:14:32,458
[LILIE groans]

283
00:14:32,541 --> 00:14:33,458
[YAYOI groans]

284
00:14:33,541 --> 00:14:35,041
Big Sister Shiho,
I've been having

285
00:14:35,125 --> 00:14:37,250
very strange dreams lately!

286
00:14:37,333 --> 00:14:39,333
Please, Big Sister!
Can we stop now?

287
00:14:39,416 --> 00:14:40,666
[SHIHO]
Shut up, you two!

288
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:43,583
We can't just give up now
after coming this far!

289
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:45,125
[SHIHO]
Huh?

290
00:14:45,208 --> 00:14:47,666
Who goes there?!

291
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,791
[CHIE] Hey there, Shiho.
Still spinning, I see?

292
00:14:53,875 --> 00:14:55,916
[gasps] Oh, if it isn't Chie!

293
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,333
Hello there!

294
00:14:57,416 --> 00:14:58,500
[CHIE]
Hm.

295
00:14:59,791 --> 00:15:02,458
[CHIE] Actually, I have
a favor to ask of you.

296
00:15:02,541 --> 00:15:03,583
What did you say?

297
00:15:03,666 --> 00:15:05,083
It seems that this information

298
00:15:05,166 --> 00:15:07,500
was originally
released by Cardair.

299
00:15:07,583 --> 00:15:09,125
[HARUKA]
Queen Mashiro is with Aswad?!

300
00:15:09,208 --> 00:15:10,625
Are you sure about that?

301
00:15:10,708 --> 00:15:13,500
Yes, this comes from
a reliable source.

302
00:15:13,583 --> 00:15:15,000
[NATSUKI]
And how's the conference going?

303
00:15:15,083 --> 00:15:17,208
We haven't been able
to reach a consensus yet,

304
00:15:17,291 --> 00:15:18,500
but I am confident

305
00:15:18,583 --> 00:15:20,250
that it's going to happen
soon, Headmistress.

306
00:15:20,333 --> 00:15:22,500
Of course, I understand.

307
00:15:22,583 --> 00:15:23,333
Nao!

308
00:15:23,416 --> 00:15:24,416
Huh?

309
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,000
We're going to Cardair.

310
00:15:26,083 --> 00:15:28,000
Are we hitchhiking again?

311
00:15:28,083 --> 00:15:30,250
[laughs]

312
00:15:30,333 --> 00:15:31,625
[growls]

313
00:15:31,708 --> 00:15:33,666
Haruka...

314
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:36,875
[sighs] Madam President,
we'll need use of a car or boat.

315
00:15:36,958 --> 00:15:37,791
[NGUYEN]
Headmistress.

316
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:38,833
Huh?

317
00:15:38,916 --> 00:15:39,958
[NGUYEN]
I have an idea.

318
00:15:40,041 --> 00:15:41,875
Why don't you leave it up to us?

319
00:15:41,958 --> 00:15:43,750
Thank you so much
for coming here!

320
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:46,333
Welcome, King Nguyen of Annam.

321
00:15:48,166 --> 00:15:50,833
[MIDORI] We don't have enough
resources to accept outsiders.

322
00:15:50,916 --> 00:15:52,458
We've already broken
our rules by allowing

323
00:15:52,541 --> 00:15:53,833
you to treat your wounded here.

324
00:15:53,916 --> 00:15:55,541
[MASHIRO] Please, can't
you make an exception?

325
00:15:55,625 --> 00:15:57,583
These people can
hardly move anymore!

326
00:15:57,666 --> 00:16:00,541
If you throw them back out
into the desert now...

327
00:16:03,916 --> 00:16:06,041
Why do you even care?

328
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:07,333
These people rejected you,

329
00:16:07,416 --> 00:16:09,833
and no longer recognize
you as their queen.

330
00:16:09,916 --> 00:16:12,750
They even went so far as
to kill your maid, right?

331
00:16:12,833 --> 00:16:14,708
Yes, I know it's all
very confusing,

332
00:16:14,791 --> 00:16:16,791
but I can't leave
them like this.

333
00:16:16,875 --> 00:16:21,541
Can you take on the burden
of all these people here?

334
00:16:21,625 --> 00:16:23,708
To save them, you
must be responsible

335
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:25,750
for all of their lives.

336
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:31,375
[ARIKA]
Mashiro!

337
00:16:31,458 --> 00:16:33,916
What's wrong?

338
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,250
No, Mimi!

339
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:39,583
A-Am I... gonna... die?

340
00:16:39,666 --> 00:16:42,083
No! No, you won't die!

341
00:16:42,166 --> 00:16:44,500
Guess... I'm being punished...

342
00:16:44,583 --> 00:16:46,041
...because of that maid.

343
00:16:46,125 --> 00:16:47,083
No!

344
00:16:47,166 --> 00:16:48,958
I'm the one to blame
for all of this!

345
00:16:49,041 --> 00:16:52,125
It's because...
It's all because of me!

346
00:16:52,208 --> 00:16:54,791
I let Aoi... and you...

347
00:16:56,208 --> 00:17:00,583
Before... everyone...
used to laugh...

348
00:17:00,666 --> 00:17:02,833
So... why...?

349
00:17:02,916 --> 00:17:04,833
Mimi...

350
00:17:04,916 --> 00:17:09,666
[gasps] Fa... ther...

351
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:13,416
I can be with you... again...

352
00:17:16,125 --> 00:17:17,500
[gasps]

353
00:17:17,583 --> 00:17:19,250
Mimi!

354
00:17:20,541 --> 00:17:24,000
Again... It's my fault.

355
00:17:32,083 --> 00:17:34,208
Everyone, please listen to me!

356
00:17:34,291 --> 00:17:37,833
I am... I am Mashiro
Blan de Windbloom.

357
00:17:37,916 --> 00:17:40,833
I am the Queen of
Windbloom Kingdom!

358
00:17:40,916 --> 00:17:43,125
I wasn't a good queen,
and because of that,

359
00:17:43,208 --> 00:17:45,500
I have caused great
pain to everyone.

360
00:17:45,583 --> 00:17:48,166
I'm sure that some of you
still despise me.

361
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:50,166
I'm truly sorry.

362
00:17:51,333 --> 00:17:52,791
But...

363
00:17:52,875 --> 00:17:55,708
If you give me another chance,
I wanna become a good queen.

364
00:17:55,791 --> 00:17:59,458
If you let me remain your ruler,
I will right my previous wrongs.

365
00:17:59,541 --> 00:18:01,916
Watch over you,
listen to the people,

366
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:05,041
and become a queen
who can properly...

367
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:07,041
...lead her people.

368
00:18:13,583 --> 00:18:15,791
I make this pledge
to you right now!

369
00:18:15,875 --> 00:18:18,500
I will use this life of mine
to protect you all!

370
00:18:18,583 --> 00:18:21,791
So please, I ask you,
entrust your lives to me!

371
00:18:30,333 --> 00:18:31,625
Leader.

372
00:18:32,958 --> 00:18:34,375
I beg you.

373
00:18:34,458 --> 00:18:36,708
Please allow these people
to stay here for a little while!

374
00:18:36,791 --> 00:18:38,208
Mashiro...

375
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:45,583
Is this a formal request
from the Queen of Windbloom?

376
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:47,500
[MASHIRO]
Mm.

377
00:18:51,958 --> 00:18:54,250
Then stand, Mashiro.

378
00:18:55,916 --> 00:18:57,458
I promise this in return.

379
00:18:57,541 --> 00:18:58,833
Once I take back my country,

380
00:18:58,916 --> 00:19:00,333
I will give you
what you want most.

381
00:19:00,416 --> 00:19:02,500
I'll give you
Garderobe's technology.

382
00:19:02,583 --> 00:19:05,208
Are you able to do that?

383
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:06,500
Yes, I am.

384
00:19:06,583 --> 00:19:09,541
I will do whatever I can.
You must believe me.

385
00:19:09,625 --> 00:19:11,166
[MIDORI]
Just remember one thing.

386
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:13,958
That anyone who betrays us...

387
00:19:14,041 --> 00:19:14,916
I know.

388
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:17,333
I swear to you, Leader of Aswad!

389
00:19:18,416 --> 00:19:20,500
Then I will believe you.

390
00:19:22,541 --> 00:19:24,250
The Queen of Windbloom.

391
00:19:24,333 --> 00:19:28,291
Our ally, Mashiro Blan
de Windbloom.

392
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:29,791
The Queen...

393
00:19:29,875 --> 00:19:32,166
[WOMAN 21C]
Queen Mashiro...

394
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:34,041
Her Majesty...

395
00:19:45,083 --> 00:19:47,125
Mimi, I'm so sorry.

396
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:50,125
If only I had done this sooner.

397
00:19:50,208 --> 00:19:53,666
The one person most responsible
for causing you all to suffer

398
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,958
is none other than me.

399
00:20:00,416 --> 00:20:04,125
Arika... this is
the last time...

400
00:20:04,208 --> 00:20:08,625
So please, just for now...
let me cry in your arms.

401
00:20:22,041 --> 00:20:25,291
From now on, I'm not
gonna cry again.

402
00:20:27,083 --> 00:20:29,208
At least, not until,
I take back my country

403
00:20:29,291 --> 00:20:31,666
and help everyone smile again.

404
00:20:33,625 --> 00:20:35,916
[MASHIRO] But I still wonder...
Can I do this?

405
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:38,166
Am I really the right
one for this task?

406
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:39,291
[ARIKA]
What do you mean?

407
00:20:39,375 --> 00:20:40,708
[MASHIRO]
Well, you might be the real

408
00:20:40,791 --> 00:20:42,291
princess of Windbloom.

409
00:20:42,375 --> 00:20:43,833
[ARIKA]
I don't think so.

410
00:20:43,916 --> 00:20:47,166
I'm not like you. I don't have
what it takes to be a queen.

411
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:48,625
Besides...

412
00:20:52,875 --> 00:20:54,583
[ARIKA]
I wanna become an Otome.

413
00:20:54,666 --> 00:20:58,166
Even though there are still many
things I don't understand...

414
00:20:58,250 --> 00:20:59,791
I wanna be able to use my power

415
00:20:59,875 --> 00:21:02,208
to protect the people
important to me!

416
00:21:02,291 --> 00:21:04,833
Then please lend me
that power of yours.

417
00:21:04,916 --> 00:21:07,208
I need your strength
as my Otome...

418
00:21:07,291 --> 00:21:10,166
No, rather, as the
Otome of Windbloom.

419
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:11,125
[ARIKA]
Mm!

420
00:21:11,208 --> 00:21:12,333
[gasps]

421
00:21:12,416 --> 00:21:13,875
That's not right.

422
00:21:17,250 --> 00:21:19,125
Yes, Master.

423
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:29,083
[meows]

424
00:21:33,625 --> 00:21:34,875
[MIDORI]
Arika.

425
00:21:34,958 --> 00:21:36,750
You once asked me
about the righteousness

426
00:21:36,833 --> 00:21:40,458
of an Otome's powers, whether
they were for good or evil.

427
00:21:40,541 --> 00:21:42,708
That is something you
decide for yourself.

428
00:21:42,791 --> 00:21:46,166
Together with your
queen by your side.

429
00:21:46,250 --> 00:21:47,291
Let's go!

430
00:21:47,375 --> 00:21:48,875
In the name of our
world of the stars,

431
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:51,666
we will carry out
our promised revenge!

432
00:22:02,375 --> 00:22:03,375
I see.

433
00:22:03,458 --> 00:22:06,041
So it looks like
they've already left.

434
00:22:06,125 --> 00:22:09,541
[CHIE] Just as you
predicted, Major Wang.

435
00:22:09,625 --> 00:22:11,416
It was more than obvious.

436
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:13,083
The information leaked.

437
00:22:13,166 --> 00:22:16,791
Emperor Argos planned to
have us fight the Aswad.

438
00:22:16,875 --> 00:22:18,250
But we don't have to.

439
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:19,875
You're too cautious.

440
00:22:19,958 --> 00:22:22,125
I wouldn't mind fighting them.

441
00:22:24,166 --> 00:22:26,291
Well, then, let us
begin our plan.

442
00:23:57,125 --> 00:23:58,541
[ARIKA]
Rad, I was wondering.

443
00:23:58,625 --> 00:24:00,250
When you're wearing your cape
what happens to your horn?

444
00:24:00,333 --> 00:24:01,458
[RAD]
Touch it and find out.

445
00:24:01,541 --> 00:24:03,166
[ARIKA]
Wow, it's soft and bendy!

446
00:24:03,250 --> 00:24:04,583
[RAD]
And it stretches, too.

447
00:24:04,666 --> 00:24:06,208
--Stretchy! Stretchy!
--[ARIKA laughs]

448
00:24:06,291 --> 00:24:08,708
--Peek-a-boo! I see you!
--[ARIKA laughs]

449
00:24:08,791 --> 00:24:11,208
[MIDORI] Rad's illness has
finally reached his brain.

